OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FIt's that time of year in LA when the
OL,7,Fphrase you're most likely to hear is:
OL,8,F"How to get that red carpet look."
OL,10,FThat's a work in progress but what is
OL,11,Fmuch easier to do is to have a guess
OL,12,Fat what this year's Oscars results
OL,13,Fmight look like.
OL,15,FI'm not sure I can remember a year
OL,16,Fwhen so many people are getting
OL,17,Finvolved in speculating about the
OL,18,Fwinners.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
