OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FAnd that is because, thank goodness,
OL,7,Fthis is genuinely a year when pretty
OL,8,Fmuch every single category except best
OL,9,Factress is just too close to call.
OL,11,FAt the beginning of the year, it was
OL,12,Fstarting to look as if it might be all
OL,13,Ftoo predictable, as in One Battle
OL,14,FAfter Another was just going to march
OL,15,Finto the ceremony and make off with
OL,16,Fall the big awards.
OL,18,FAs if Timothee Chalamet was totally
OL,19,Fgoing to be taking his best actor
OL,20,FOscar home with to his celebrity
OL,21,Fgirlfriend.
OL,26,@zD@Mrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
