OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FBut what a difference a few weeks
OL,7,Fmake. Now even the best picture
OL,8,Fcategory is a very tight race, and
OL,9,Fit's just the kind of buildup that the
OL,10,FOscars producers will be loving,
OL,11,Fbecause no one wants to sit through
OL,12,Fthree hours knowing full well what the
OL,13,Fmajor rewards at the end of the night
OL,14,Fare going to look like.
OL,16,FSo, these are my predictions for just
OL,17,Fa few of the categories. I could so
OL,18,Feasily be wrong in all of these, and
OL,19,Fthat's what should make this year's
OL,20,FOscars a great watch:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
