OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FThe foregone conclusion for many
OL,7,Fmonths is that Paul Thomas Anderson's
OL,8,Fepic One Battle After Another is going
OL,9,Fto get this, but with a record
OL,10,Fbreaking 16 Oscar nominations for
OL,11,FSinners, this is going to prove
OL,12,Fgenuinely nail-biting when the
OL,13,Fcategory is announced on stage at the
OL,14,FDolby Theatre on Sunday.
OL,16,FWill win: One Battle After Another. I
OL,17,Fthink it will still win this but only
OL,18,Fjust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
