OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FShould win: Sinners. A genuinely
OL,7,Fsurprising and ambitious piece of work
OL,8,Fyou just won't see anything else like
OL,9,Fthis.
OL,11,FPaul Thomas Anderson has had 14 Oscar
OL,12,Fnominations in all. The revered
OL,13,Fdirector has never won one yet, but
OL,14,Fthe Academy will put that right this
OL,15,Fweekend I'm sure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
