OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FWill win: Paul Thomas Anderson. His
OL,7,Fbody of work is stunning, and it is
OL,8,Funbelievable that he has never won
OL,9,Fbest director before after all this is
OL,10,Fthe man who made one of my favourite
OL,11,Ffilms, Licorice Pizza.
OL,13,FShould win: Paul Thomas Anderson. Give
OL,14,Fthe man an Oscar for goodness' sake.
OL,15,Fthough if this were to go to Ryan
OL,16,FCoogler the director of Sinners, I
OL,17,Fwould be equally happy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
