OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FNow this is going to be an extremely
OL,7,Finteresting category. For a long time,
OL,8,Fit seemed as if this was going to be
OL,9,FLeonardo DiCaprio's year, then it
OL,10,Flooked like it was going to be
OL,11,FTimothee Chalamet's year.
OL,13,FIn fact, up to a few weeks ago, it
OL,14,Flooked like the latter had this one in
OL,15,Fthe bag for his great performance in
OL,16,FMarty Supreme.
OL,18,FBut this is looking increasingly
OL,19,Funlikely and not because of those ill-
OL,20,Ftimed comments he made on ballet and
OL,21,Fopera.
