OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FThose comments only became public in
OL,7,Fthe media around the same time that
OL,8,FOscar voting closed so they will not
OL,9,Fhave greatly impacted the way the
OL,10,FAcademy voted.
OL,12,FWill win: Michael B Jordan. He's just
OL,13,Fsuperb in his dual roles in Sinners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
