OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FHe so deserves this, and maybe there
OL,7,Fis a feeling that after what happened
OL,8,Fat the Baftas, when he and Delroy
OL,9,FLindo were on stage and a racial slur
OL,10,Fwas shouted from the auditorium by a
OL,11,Fguest with Tourette's syndrome, which
OL,12,Fwas then aired by the BBC, he is
OL,13,Fworthy of some sympathy.
OL,15,FThough for me first and foremost he
OL,16,Fdeserves the best actor Oscar because
OL,17,Fhe's brilliant in this film.
OL,19,FShould win: Michael B. Jordan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
