OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FJessie Buckley has simply been
OL,7,Fsweeping up every award going for her
OL,8,Frole in Hamnet.
OL,10,FIf she doesn't get this, it'll be one
OL,11,Fof the biggest upsets in recent Oscars
OL,12,Fhistory.
OL,14,FA note of caution: Rose Byrne is
OL,15,Fgathering a lot of support here for
OL,16,Fher fantastic performance in If I Had
OL,17,FLegs, I'd Kick You. Either of these
OL,18,Fwould be worthy winners.
OL,20,FWill win: Jessie Buckley. A flawless
OL,21,Fperformance which carried the film.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
