OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FShould win: Jessie Buckley
OL,8,FNow, this is an interesting category.
OL,9,FI know popular opinion right now seems
OL,10,Fto suggest that this one is for Sean
OL,11,FPenn, for One Battle, a role he's been
OL,12,Fawarded for this season.
OL,14,FBut what about Stellan Skarsgard in
OL,15,FSentimental Value? Earlier on an award
OL,16,Fseason it seemed like this would be
OL,17,Fhis, though in my opinion he is more
OL,18,Fof a lead actor than a supporting
OL,19,Factor in that film so his selection
OL,20,Ffor this category is rather puzzling.
