OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FAnd could Benicio Del Toro split the
OL,7,Fvotes as he's also nominated for One
OL,8,FBattle?
OL,10,FWill win: Sean Penn ` although this is
OL,11,Fa tough one to call.
OL,13,FShould win: Delroy Lindo. He is
OL,14,Fpeerless in Sinners.
OL,16,FThis is another really interesting
OL,17,Fcategory and incredibly competitive,
OL,18,Fin fact any of the nominees could walk
OL,19,Faway with this award on the night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
