OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FIt feels like there's been a late
OL,7,Fsurge of support for Teyana Taylor in
OL,8,FOne Battle After Another, and if that
OL,9,Ffilm wins in many of the other
OL,10,Fcategories, this could be hers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
