OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FHer competition will come from Wunmi
OL,7,FMosaku, and it would be wonderful to
OL,8,Fsee her win, especially if Delroy
OL,9,FLindo triumphs as best supporting
OL,10,Factor because that will mean that
OL,11,FBritain has had two acting wins at the
OL,12,FOscars (sorry Delroy I know that you
OL,13,Fhave spent most of your life in
OL,14,FAmerica, but you were born in Lewisham
OL,15,Fin South London so we are going to
OL,16,Fclaim you anyway).
OL,18,FBut I do feel that an industry
OL,19,Ffavourite who has waited four decades
OL,20,Fsince her last nomination may just pip
OL,21,Feveryone at the post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
