OL,3,COscar Awards 2026: Our predictions for
OL,4,Cthis year's winners
OL,6,FWill win: Amy Madigan. She is a thing
OL,7,Fof wonder in the horror film Weapons.
OL,9,FShould win: While my heart says Wunmi
OL,10,FMosaku, I do feel that Amy Madigan
OL,11,Fshould be awarded for her performance.
